short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Participate in the SALIENT Sustained trial for healthier people and planet

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension was developed for study participants in one of the SALIENT Food system trials. The research is led by the Universities of Oxford, Cambridge, and Warwick, and Queen Mary University London, and is conducted in collaboration with Prolific consultants.
Participants: Please click “Add to Chrome” above to install the extension.
